<section class="page">
  <div class="wrap narrow">
    <span class="eyebrow">Safety &amp; Consent</span>
    <h1 class="mt-2 mb-3">Your safety comes first</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">The lifestyle runs on respect and enthusiastic consent. Here's how we help you stay safe — and what we expect from every member.</p>

    <div class="card card-pad mb-3">
      <h3 class="mb-2">Consent is everything</h3>
      <p class="muted">No means no — from anyone, at any time, for any reason. Pressuring, coercing, or ignoring boundaries is grounds for immediate removal.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card card-pad mb-3">
      <h3 class="mb-2">Protect your identity</h3>
      <p class="muted">Use a handle, not your legal name. Keep face photos private until you trust someone. Never share financial details — no legitimate member will ask.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card card-pad mb-3">
      <h3 class="mb-2">Meet smart</h3>
      <p class="muted">Meet first in a public place. Tell a friend where you're going. Trust your instincts — if something feels off, leave.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card card-pad mb-3">
      <h3 class="mb-2">Block &amp; report</h3>
      <p class="muted">One tap blocks a member so you'll never see each other again. Reports go to a real human review team. Abuse, harassment, or anyone who appears underage is removed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card card-pad">
      <h3 class="mb-2">Strictly 18+</h3>
      <p class="muted">Every member confirms they are a legal adult. Any suspicion of a minor is reported to the appropriate authorities. There is zero tolerance.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="text-sm muted mt-4">Concerns? Contact <a href="mailto:<%= brand.supportEmail %>" class="text-gold"><%= brand.supportEmail %></a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>
